{"ID":"20240821093050-zyblovj","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20240821093050-zyblovj","title":"如果我想自己设置一个链接器脚本应该怎么弄 ","type":"doc","updated":"20240924142855"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240821093052-334qpwc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-334qpwc","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"编写和使用自定义链接器脚本涉及几个步骤，包括理解内存布局、编写链接器脚本、配置编译器使用该脚本以及进行调试。以下是详细的流程："}]},{"ID":"20240821093052-319cqaf","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-319cqaf","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1. "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"理解目标平台的内存布局"}]},{"ID":"20240821093052-6gi0dds","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-6gi0dds","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240821093052-45wro0w","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-45wro0w","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240821093052-jfr4ldz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-jfr4ldz","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"了解目标芯片的内存结构"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：阅读芯片的手册，了解可用的内存区域（如 Flash、SRAM）的起始地址和大小。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240821093052-3mf4ufi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-3mf4ufi","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240821093052-16g1fn0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-16g1fn0","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"确定代码和数据的存放位置"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：决定程序的不同部分（如代码段、数据段、堆栈等）应该存放在哪些内存区域。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20240821093052-ucf774k","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-ucf774k","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2. "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"编写链接器脚本"}]},{"ID":"20240821093052-qfwbbnt","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-qfwbbnt","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240821093052-v76wrl5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-v76wrl5","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240821093052-kyvlhl9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-kyvlhl9","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"链接器脚本通常使用 GNU "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"ld"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 的语法来定义内存布局和符号。典型的链接器脚本包含以下几个部分："}]},{"ID":"20240821093052-6zgqey4","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-6zgqey4","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240821093052-gd5n040","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-gd5n040","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240821093052-931peky","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-931peky","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"定义内存区域"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：指定每个内存区域的起始地址和大小。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240821093052-jozdpsm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-jozdpsm","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240821093052-lq9avne","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-lq9avne","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"定义段的布局"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：定义代码段（如 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":".text"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 段）、数据段（如 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":".data"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 和 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":".bss"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 段）、堆栈、堆等的存放位置。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240821093052-4xqaoxu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-4xqaoxu","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240821093052-9v54p7l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-9v54p7l","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"输出格式"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：指定输出文件的格式。"}]}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20240821093052-q3qo7xe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-q3qo7xe","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"示例链接器脚本"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"："}]},{"ID":"20240821093052-pzbjj29","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-pzbjj29","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"bGQ="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"/* 定义内存区域 */\nMEMORY\n{\n    FLASH (rx) : ORIGIN = 0x08000000, LENGTH = 512K\n    SRAM (rwx) : ORIGIN = 0x20000000, LENGTH = 128K\n}\n\n/* 设置入口点 */\nENTRY(Reset_Handler)\n\n/* 分段定义 */\nSECTIONS\n{\n    /* 将 .text 段放置在 FLASH 区域 */\n    .text : \n    {\n        *(.isr_vector) /* 中断向量表 */\n        *(.text*)      /* 所有代码段 */\n        *(.rodata*)    /* 只读数据 */\n        _etext = .;    /* 记录 .text 段结束地址 */\n    } \u003eFLASH\n\n    /* 将 .data 段放置在 SRAM 区域 */\n    .data : \n    {\n        _sdata = .;    /* 数据段开始地址 */\n        *(.data*)\n        _edata = .;    /* 数据段结束地址 */\n    } \u003eSRAM AT\u003e FLASH\n\n    /* 将 .bss 段放置在 SRAM 区域 */\n    .bss : \n    {\n        _sbss = .;     /* 未初始化数据段开始地址 */\n        *(.bss*)\n        _ebss = .;     /* 未初始化数据段结束地址 */\n    } \u003eSRAM\n\n    /* 栈的定义 */\n    .stack (NOLOAD) : \n    {\n        . = ALIGN(4);\n        _sstack = .;\n        . = . + 0x2000;  /* 分配 8KB 作为堆栈 */\n        _estack = .;\n    } \u003eSRAM\n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240821093052-uh17swu","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-uh17swu","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3. "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"配置编译器使用自定义链接器脚本"}]},{"ID":"20240821093052-s7gcyrt","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-s7gcyrt","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240821093052-oxnv1xr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-oxnv1xr","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240821093052-s5bg8ho","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-s5bg8ho","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"修改编译选项"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：大多数编译器允许你通过命令行选项指定自定义链接器脚本。例如，使用 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"arm-none-eabi-gcc"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 编译时，你可以使用以下命令："}]},{"ID":"20240821093052-vc46b21","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-vc46b21","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"c2g="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"arm-none-eabi-gcc -T your_linker_script.ld -o output.elf ...\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]}]},{"ID":"20240821093052-k5ay3ta","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-k5ay3ta","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240821093052-du95c14","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-du95c14","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"集成到构建系统"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：如果你使用了 Makefile 或其他构建系统工具，可以在其中指定链接器脚本路径。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20240821093052-3dkvrso","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-3dkvrso","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4. "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"编译并生成目标文件"}]},{"ID":"20240821093052-txmykne","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-txmykne","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240821093052-cf2ds6u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-cf2ds6u","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240821093052-d1bhy7t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-d1bhy7t","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"使用编译器进行编译和链接，将源代码链接到指定的内存位置。输出的 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":".elf"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 文件将包含你定义的内存布局。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20240821093052-6kc42rb","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-6kc42rb","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5. "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"调试与验证"}]},{"ID":"20240821093052-cxhj5g6","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-cxhj5g6","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240821093052-pxz171n","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-pxz171n","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240821093052-m844in1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-m844in1","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"使用调试器或仿真器（如 GDB）加载生成的 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":".elf"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 文件，并验证程序是否正确运行，检查各段是否正确加载到预期的内存地址。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240821093052-krkk660","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-krkk660","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240821093052-629vckq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-629vckq","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"检查编译器输出的内存映射文件（通常是 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":".map"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 文件）来确认各段的地址和大小。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20240821093052-hr4g4ab","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-hr4g4ab","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"6. "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"调整与优化"}]},{"ID":"20240821093052-to2fnmc","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-to2fnmc","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240821093052-4ic187c","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-4ic187c","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240821093052-zx7m5jf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-zx7m5jf","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"根据调试和测试的结果，可能需要调整链接器脚本中的设置。例如，如果堆栈溢出或堆空间不足，可能需要调整堆栈和堆的大小。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240821093052-2wjxadw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-2wjxadw","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240821093052-uqzr1ai","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-uqzr1ai","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"反复修改和测试，直到程序在目标硬件上稳定运行。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20240821093052-bca4kjn","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-bca4kjn","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"总结"}]},{"ID":"20240821093052-chyfivb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240821093052-chyfivb","updated":"20240821093052"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"编写链接器脚本是一个复杂但非常有用的过程，特别是在嵌入式系统开发中。通过理解内存布局，编写合适的链接器脚本，并进行调试和优化，你可以精确控制程序在目标硬件上的行为。"}]}]}